4.title: Recall
4.content:
Please point to the pictures you just saw, in the order they were presented. If your visor was down, please raise it now.
When you have chosen all you can remember, please click Done to continue.

6.title: Get-set-go
6.content:
Ready?

In a moment, we're going to show you some pictures. Please try to remember them as best you can. You'll be asked to remember them in the order in which you saw the pictures.

When you're ready, please press Continue below.

8.title: Picture Presentation
8.content:
Please say the name of the pictures you see.
Experimenter, please press "y" if they named the picture, and "n" if they did not.

10.title: Welcome
10.content:
Welcome!

We are going to play a picture game with you. We want you to show us your memory for some pictures. You will also sometimes wear a cool helmet!



When you're ready, please press Continue below.

11.title: Strategy
11.content:
How did you do this task?
When you saw the pictures, you knew
you were supposed to try to remember them,
so you could point to the same ones afterward, right?
What did you do to remember them? How did you go
about trying to keep them straight in your head?

Please tell us how you tried to remember the pictures.



Please check the box, or boxes, below, if needed to clarify any of the above.


I said the picture names to myself, one at a time.


I said the picture names to myself, over and over, adding on a new picture each time.


I thought about the way the pictures looked.


I did not do anything special to remember them.


Something else.

13.title: Visor Practice
13.content:
Visor Practice!

Please spend some time getting comfortable in the helmet. We want you to try putting the visor down. Let's try having it down for 5 seconds.
Then, we want you to raise the visor. We will say, "visor up!".
Let's give it a try.
Then, let's try 10 seconds with the visor down. Ok?
Finally, let's try 15 seconds. That's the longest the visor will be down during our game.


When you're ready, please press Continue below.

14.title: Goodbye Screen
14.content: Thank you for being in the experiment!

16.title: Trial sequence for Point and Name

17.title: Get-set-go
17.content:
Ready?

In a moment, we're going to show you some pictures. Please point to and name each picture out loud as you see it. Then try to remember them as best you can. You'll be asked to remember them in the order in which you saw them. When you point to them, please say the name of the picture out loud.

When you're ready, please press Continue below.
